A small 2-player human-vs-human soccer game inspired by
the classic Amiga game Sensible Soccer.

Requires PyGame.
To run:
    $ python start.py

Keys:
    -----------------------------------------------------
    What              Player 1              Player 2
    -----------------------------------------------------
    Move the player   up/down/left/right    a/s/d/w
    Kick the ball     . (period)            ` (backquote)
    -/=               Zoom in and out
